<a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=67393">Solanthious the Wind Caller</a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ubraskdembones.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Brask Dembones</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>h0x0r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(10/19/01 5:37:36 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HoT on Calendar???</span><hr size=1> Sol, this had nothing to do specifically with the raid that night and I wasn't even there for the initial start time so I was completely unaware that you guys had even spoken.  Like I said in my first post, I'm not here to blame anyone, this would be in Rants or SL if I was doing that.<br>
<br>
I got on-line and found out it was cancelled.  All I heard was that they went in, saw you guys in there and decided to call it off.  So let's please leave it at that <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
